<l>veṉvēl..................................natu</l>
<l>muṉṟiṟ kiṭanta peruṅkaḷi yāḷaṟ</l>
<l>kataḷuṇ ṭāyiṉum pāyuṇṭāyiṉum</l>
<l>yātuṇ ṭāyiṉuṅ koṭumiṉ vallē</l>
<l>vēṭkai mīḷapa .......</l>
<l>..............ku memakkum piṟarkkum</l>
<l>yārkku mīyntu tuyilēṟ piṉaṉē.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
